  • public class isLeveledHighSchool
extends SchoolTest
    Test with no students, with one, and many. Use of decision coverage technique by creating: - No prepared students only (which should return false) - Prepared students only (should return true) - No students at all (returns false) - Mix of students (which should be different for each of them)
